text: Courtney Melba Barnett (born 3 November 1987) is an Australian singer- songwriter and guitarist from Melbourne. Barnett was born in Tasmania. Barnett started playing guitar when she was 10. Barnett starts a UK tour in May. ==Other websites== *Official website ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Australian singer-songwriters Category:Living people
